"26:36:2" : {s: 26, a: 36, w: 2, r: "رجو", t: "أَرْجِهْ", l: "تُرْجِى", lc: 3, tl: "arjih", lb: "স্থগিত করা, বিলম্বিত করণ,",e: "Postpone him", b: "অবকাশ দাও", i: "tangguhkan dia", f: 2, rm: "to hope/expect, an opinion requiring the happening of an event in which will be a cause of happiness; expectation of deriving advantage from an event of which a cause has already occurred, keep awaited, put off, put aside, defer/delay, fear, beg/request. arja (pl.) - borders, sides. marjowwon is a person in whom great hopes are placed (e.g. 11:62).", ag: "فعل أمر صيغة ٤ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Imperative 4th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPV", qual: "(IV)", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "مُرْجَوْنَ،يَرْجُوا۟،تُرْجِى"},
